results.description: Found this guy a couple of years back. This was one of my favorite observations from that trip. These are one of the cutest sparrows I have seen in my life. There was a couple of girls that scared it off but for a moment I could catch a few photos of this very pretty bird. It is not spotted like other sparrows I am familiar with. I love the markings on this bird.
